rComments: He gives good feedback on all the assignments. The lectures can get a bit dry at times and he does force discussions and breakout rooms during class.

Very smart and very reasonable Prof. He encourages you to take the subject matter and make it your own. He does not hesitate to give you 90+ when it's deserved. A very relevant and interesting course - recommended to every student!
He's a really easy grader, no final or midterm. He is super fast at grading work and grades easily. He's pretty clear on what he wants, would definitely recommend for this class
